---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Training - Fabien Salles" 
  description="Discover my training courses on software craftsmanship, Clean Code, and development best practices"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Training</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg mb-12">
      <p>
        I offer customized training to help your teams improve their skills
        in software craftsmanship practices. My training sessions are practical,
        interactive, and adapted to your specific needs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <a href="/en/training/clean-code" class="p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Clean Code</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Learn Clean Code principles to write more maintainable,
            readable, and robust code.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• SOLID principles</li>
            <li>• Code naming and organization</li>
            <li>• Refactoring</li>
            <li>• Technical debt</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 2-3 days</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
            Learn more →
          </span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/en/training/tdd" class="p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Test-Driven Development</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Master TDD to develop more reliable and
            easier to maintain applications.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Red-green-refactor cycle</li>
            <li>• Unit testing</li>
            <li>• Integration testing</li>
            <li>• Mocking and test doubles</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 2 days</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
            Learn more →
          </span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Hexagonal Architecture</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Discover how to structure your applications to make them more
            modular and testable.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Hexagonal architecture principles</li>
            <li>• Business domain</li>
            <li>• Adapters and ports</li>
            <li>• Practical cases</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 2 days</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Custom Training</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        I can adapt my training to your specific needs and your team's level.
        Don't hesitate to contact me to discuss your goals.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/en/contact" 
        class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        Contact me
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>